    <title>How to start a blog.</title>
    <url>/2021/03/08/2021-03-08-How-to-start-a-blog/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="Install-Node-js"><a href="#Install-Node-js" class="headerlink" title="Install Node.js."></a><strong>Install Node.js.</strong></h1><h3 id="Download-Node-js-from-the-official-website"><a href="#Download-Node-js-from-the-official-website" class="headerlink" title="Download Node.js from the official website."></a><strong>Download Node.js from the official website.</strong></h3><p><strong>Check Node.js using the following code</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>node -v</strong></li>
<li><strong>npm -v</strong></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 id="Install-Git"><a href="#Install-Git" class="headerlink" title="Install Git."></a><strong>Install Git.</strong></h1><h3 id="Download-Git-from-the-official-website"><a href="#Download-Git-from-the-official-website" class="headerlink" title="Download Git from the official website."></a><strong>Download Git from the official website.</strong></h3><p><strong>Check Git using the following code</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>git –version</strong></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 id="Install-Hexo"><a href="#Install-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="Install Hexo."></a><strong>Install Hexo.</strong></h1><h3 id="Download-Hexo-using-the-following-code"><a href="#Download-Hexo-using-the-following-code" class="headerlink" title="Download Hexo using the following code."></a><strong>Download Hexo using the following code.</strong></h3><ul>
<li><strong>npm install -g hexo–cli</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Check Hexo using the following code</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>hexo -v</strong></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 id="Initialize-Hexo"><a href="#Initialize-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="Initialize Hexo."></a><strong>Initialize Hexo.</strong></h1><ul>
<li><p><strong>Create a floder（eg. name= “blog”）</strong></p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>git bash/ cmd  —— blog</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>hexo init “floder” (eg. name= “myblog”)</strong></p>
<p><strong>cd “floder”</strong></p>
<p><strong>npm install</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h1 id="Web-page-preview"><a href="#Web-page-preview" class="headerlink" title="Web page preview"></a><strong>Web page preview</strong></h1><ul>
<li><p><strong>hexo generate (Generating the static web page)</strong></p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>hexo server (The preview page)</strong></p>
</li>
<li><p><strong><a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000</a></strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 id="Deploy-to-github-pages"><a href="#Deploy-to-github-pages" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to github pages"></a><strong>Deploy to github pages</strong></h1><ul>
<li><strong>create a github account</strong></li>
<li><strong>cerate a new repository</strong></li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>repository name= “username.github.io”</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><strong>generate SSH in git bash</strong></li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>git config –global user.name “yourname”</strong></p>
<p><strong>git config –global user.email “youremail”</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Check  using the following code</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>git config user.name</strong></li>
<li><strong>git config user.email</strong></li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C “youremail”</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><strong>get the ssh public key</strong></li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>C/user/yourname/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><strong>paste to github</strong></li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Check  using the following code</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>ssh -T <a href="mailto:&#103;&#105;&#116;&#x40;&#x67;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#117;&#98;&#x2e;&#99;&#111;&#109;">&#103;&#105;&#116;&#x40;&#x67;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#117;&#98;&#x2e;&#99;&#111;&#109;</a></strong></li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><strong>modify site file</strong></li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>_config.yml</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>deploy:</strong></p>
<p>​    <strong>type: git</strong></p>
<p>​    <strong>repo: <a href="https://github.com/yourname/yourname.github.io.git">https://github.com/yourname/yourname.github.io.git</a></strong></p>
<p>​    <strong>branch: main</strong></p>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><strong>install deploy-git</strong></li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>npm install hexo-deployer-git –save</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><strong>deploy</strong></li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>hexo generate</strong></p>
<p><strong>hexo deploy</strong></p>
<p><strong><a href="https://1487790559.github.io/">https://1487790559.github.io</a></strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p>hello <a href="https://scoheart.github.io/2021/03/08/2021-03-08-How-to-start-a-blog/">https://Scoheart.github.io/2021/03/08/2021-03-08-How-to-start-a-blog/</a> bye</p>
]]></content>
